Package: rkainu
Title: Finnish Spirometry Reference Values (Kainu et al. 2015)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Rikhard", "Mäki-Heikkilä", , "rikhard.maki-heikkila@tuni.fi", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Predicted values, z-scores, lower limits of normal (LLN), and
    percent-predicted for Finnish adult spirometry using the Kainu et al. (2015)
    reference equations. Covers FVC, FEV1, FEV1/FVC, FEV6, FEV1/FEV6, PEF,
    MMEF, MEF75, MEF50, and MEF25 for adults aged 18-90. The API mirrors
    'rspiro' for easy side-by-side comparison with GLI-2012 reference values.
